T02D3594:219b-1: badzra gandha r'i s'a dha nam /
T02D3594:219b-3: rdo rje gandha ri'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3594:219b-4: 'phags ma rdo rje g'andh'a r'i la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3594:219b-5: rdo rje gandha r'i nag mo zhal drug pa /
T02D3594:219b-7: dbu skra kham pa gyen du brdzes shing zhabs g-yon brkyang pa'o //
T02D3594:219b-9: zhal so so la spyan gsum gsum pa /
T02D3594:219b-10: phyag g-yas pa drug na go rims bzhin du rdo rje dang /
T02D3594:219b-14: mda' dang 'khor lo rnams bsnams pa /
T02D3594:219b-15: phyag g-yon pa drug na kha tv'am ga dang /
T02D3594:219b-21: zhal dang po ni nag po'o //
T02D3594:219b-22: zhal gzhan rnams ni kha dog lnga ste /
T02D3594:219b-28: sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
T02D3594:219b-30: aom h'um h'um h'um sv'a h'a /
